<doc id="20646765" url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=20646765" title="Turkey Creek, Florida">
Turkey Creek, Florida

Turkey Creek is a rural, unincorporated community located in eastern Hillsborough County, Florida. The community is served by a 33527 ZIP Code.
Geography.
Palm River is located at 27.977 North, 82.185 West, or about 3 miles west-southwest of Plant City. The elevation of the community is 92 feet above sea level.
Description.
Turkey Creek approximate boundaries include Dover to the west, Interstate 4 to the north, Plant City to the east, and State Road 60 to the south.

