<doc id="20646871" url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=20646871" title="Skye Stracke">
Skye Stracke

Skye Stracke is an Australian fashion model from Perth, Western Australia.
Career.
Prior to her career as a model, Stracke wanted to be a makeup artist. She won a modeling competition at Vivien's, an Australian modeling agency, and walked in Rosemount Australian Fashion Week, where she was scouted by DNA Model Management. 
She moved to New York City on 9 January 2008 to further her modeling career.
She subsequently walked in shows for Chanel, Christian Lacroix, Nina Ricci (brand), and Missoni, and has shot editorials for American and Russian "Vogue (magazine)". She has also modeled for a Lacoste campaign.

